Introduction

In this report we compare experimental and theoretical SDi profiles and SDi profiles with MSFi and 1/CN. We show the figures of all families. Then, we compare correlations between SDi profiles with the number of proteins of the family and the sites of p.ref. Finally, we comapre correlations obtained for SDi theo profiles with correlations obtained for LPD.
